{
  "stem": "12674.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to-- we could to take our clothes and some bedding and things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not even furniture, not-- not-- bedding, linens, and blankets, but not mattresses and not beds.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had to just leave everything behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so we-- we got another apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't really an apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a building next to the big temple in Vienna where they had sort of an office building there, where they had schools of Talmud, Torah, and other things.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they used some of the offices, and they made homes out of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were a couple of big apartments in that building, you know, like eight-, nine-room apartments like they used to have at that time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they gave everybody a bedroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Each family had a bedroom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there were all the families that were in this apartment would use one kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that's how we lived from 1939 until-- we had two rooms, one living room-size sort of room and one little room, like a one-window room.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in one-- in the big room, there was in one corner, there was a-- a a cook-- a wooden cook stove, and that was our kitchen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pretty much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, actually, it was-- I don't know because I didn't finish the year because I caught scarlet fever, and I was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't know whether they were in school until June or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know in April I stopped going to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was very, very soon after that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the-- the teacher saying something about the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, even at 12.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember saying to her, we want to leave, but you're not letting us go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you don't like us, why don't you let us go?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
